Constructor Detail

SpaceOperatorSet

public SpaceOperatorSet(SpaceOperator interiorSpaceOperator,
                        SpaceOperator exteriorSpaceOperator)
Creates a SpaceOperatorSet with the given space operators. Either may be null if no space operator was specified in which case inheritFrom(SpaceOperatorSet) can be used to inherit the corresponding space operator from a parent SpaceOperatorSet.

Parameters:
interiorSpaceOperator - the interior space operator, or null if no interior space operator was specified.
exteriorSpaceOperator - the interior space operator, or null if no exterior space operator was specified.

with

public SpaceOperatorSet with(SpaceOperator newInteriorSpaceOperator,
                             SpaceOperator newExteriorSpaceOperator)
Returns:
a SpaceOperatorSet with the interior and exterior space operators set as specified. As an optimization, if the result would be equivalent to this SpaceOperatorSet then this SpaceOperatorSet is returned.

inheritFrom

public SpaceOperatorSet inheritFrom(SpaceOperatorSet parent)
Returns:
a SpaceOperatorSet that is the same as this one except that any operator that is non-null will be inherited from the supplied "parent" in the result SpaceOperatorSet.
